description: Even though the city centre - especially the Wenceslas Square - is crowded with young tourists I almost never stopped one. But today when I checked an area which is not so popular amongst tourist I met a British or American boy. He seemed quite nice but he was too worried or just arrogant to pay attention to my offers. Who knows. Then I met a cool guy who run butt-naked through a crowded street. For 1,000 crowns. And when I saw his friend coming along I thought I met an angel. A real cutie with a heard-braking smile. And as he moved from Ostrava to Prague for his studies he was interested in making money. And I wasn´t a miser this time. I decided for myself: this boy is gonna be mine.
title: Czech Hunter 113
